The paper deals with policy optimization for finding Nash equilibria in zero-sum linear quadratic games, which is a problem in reinforcement learning and game theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.RO (Robotics).
